    "description": "BIO-LGCA is a cellular automaton modelling class for analyzing collective cell migration.\nTo overcome drawbacks of classical on-lattice models, we introduce a novel on-lattice, agent-based modelling class for collective cell migration, which we call biological lattice-gas cellular automaton (BIO-LGCA). The BIO-LGCA is characterised by synchronous time updates and the explicit consideration of individual cell velocities.",
